imdb.plot outline: Each two-minute episode of this scripted digital series features a savvy beauty guru from a bygone era showing you how to DIY the latest beauty craze. From "crocodile dung face masks" in Ancient Greece to turn of the century "arsenic complexion wafers," this show covers everything from the totally weird to the downright dangerous. These are REAL historical make up practices. We're not even kidding.
